                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
            </nav>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="hero">
                    <h1>A place to keep <br> records of <span>book</span> <br> you read.</h1>
                    <form action=""><button type="submit" class="new-book-btn"><svg class="plus icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" />
                      </svg>
                      new book</button></form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <section id="books">
            <div class="books">
                <div class="book-container">
                    <div class="book-summary">
                        <p>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quia commodi sapiente voluptates tempora itaque cum non repellendus? Commodi id eveniet, distinctio quas vero repellat vitae quia hic, impedit, iure animi.
                        Facilis minus esse tenetur id? Ratione, illo explicabo, nostrum quia odio dolore aliquam quos eveniet sit possimus placeat fugit reprehenderit id iusto, ipsam modi cum dolor aut magni sunt magnam?
                        Officia totam veritatis recusandae, ex nostrum sequi odit! Magnam non a voluptates saepe doloremque maxime, natus tenetur ullam animi ea accusantium praesentium et illum! Ad aperiam nemo consequatur illum autem.
                        Rerum nisi enim, delectus necessitatibus non ad u illum quasi assumenda excepturi deserunt placeat, quos ipsam nemo voluptate nesciunt ut error obcaecati. Rem?
                       </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="book-details">
                        <div class="book-info">
                            <h3 class="book-name">Psychology of Money</h3>
                            <h5 class="author">Morgan Housel</h5>
                            <h6 class="date">Date : 18/12/2012 Wednesday</h6>
                            <h6 class="isbn">SBIN : 123456767</h6>
                            <h6 class="rating">Rating : 10/10</h6>
                            <div class="buy-read-btn-div">
                                <button class="read-more buy-read-btn">Read more</button>
                                <button class="buy-online buy-read-btn">Buy Online</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <img src="/images/morgan-housel-aZ_MmSmAcjg-unsplash-removebg-preview.png" alt="book-cvr-img" class="book-cvr-img">
